'''逆行射精'''（{{lang-en|Retrograde ejaculation}}）指的是在正常[[性交|性交]]過程中，男性在有射精的感覺和動作后，[[精液|精液]]沒有正常從尿道射出，反而逆行射入[[膀胱|膀胱]]的一種疾病。由於射精過程由[[膀胱頸|膀胱頸]][[括約肌|括約肌]]控制，因此逆行射精可能與括約肌的虛弱或神經控制異常有關。<ref name="merck">{{Cite web|title=Retrograde Ejaculation - Men's Health Issues|url=https://www.merckmanuals.com/home/men-s-health-issues/sexual-dysfunction-in-men/retrograde-ejaculation|accessdate=2020-12-25|work=Merck Manuals Consumer Version|language=en-US}}</ref>此外，逆行射精也有可能與{{le|射精管梗阻|Ejaculatory duct obstruction}}、[[經尿道前列腺切除術|經尿道前列腺切除術]]有聯繫。

逆行射精常常與所謂的“[[性高潮#男性|無射精高潮]]”聯繫在一起，是[[男性不育|男性不育]]的原因之一。<ref name="fertilityfactor">{{Cite web|title=Male Infertility: Retrograde Ejaculation|url=https://www.fertilityfactor.com/infertility_male_infertility_retrograde_ejaculation.html|accessdate=2020-12-25|work=www.fertilityfactor.com}}</ref>

==病因==
膀胱頸括約肌相關的逆行射精大致可分為[[自主神經系統|自主神經系統]]功能紊亂及前列腺問題這兩類，[[高血壓|高血壓]]、[[良性前列腺增生|良性前列腺增生]]（包括治療此病使用的[[坦索羅辛|坦索羅辛]]）、[[情緒病|情緒病]]、前列腺手術和[[神經損傷|神經損傷]]都可能會造成逆行射精。<ref>[http://www.retrogradeejaculation.net/ Retrograde Ejaculation Causes, Symptoms and Treatment] {{Wayback|url=http://www.retrogradeejaculation.net/|date=20190413150949}} Retrieved on 2010-03-02</ref><ref name="Jukes2002">{{cite book|last=Jukes|first=Mavis|authorlink=Mavis Jukes|title=The guy book: an owner's manual for teens: safety, maintenance, and operating instructions for teens|url=https://archive.org/details/guybookowners00juke|year=2002|publisher=Crown Publishers|location=New York|isbn=0-679-89028-9|page=[https://archive.org/details/guybookowners00juke/page/16 16]}}</ref>據統計，其中膀胱頸手術是十分之一的逆行射精的病因<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Mini symposium: non-surgical sperm recovery: Part II. Treatment of retrograde ejaculation and anejaculation|url=https://academic.oup.com/humupd/article-lookup/doi/10.1093/humupd/5.5.448|last=Kamischke|first=A|date=1999-09-01|journal=Human Reproduction Update|issue=5|doi=10.1093/humupd/5.5.448|volume=5|pages=448–474|language=en|issn=1355-4786}}</ref>。此外的常見病因還有服用[[抗精神病药|安定藥]]和[[抗抑鬱劑|抗抑鬱劑]]，不過大多數病人在停止服藥后逆行射精的問題就會自動解決。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Patologie trattate: Eiaculazione retrograda e Aneiaculazione|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080208145058/http://www.giovannialei.it/patologie/eiaculazione_retrograda.htm#|accessdate=2020-12-25|publisher=Prof. Giovanni Alei|language=it|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080208145058/http://www.giovannialei.it/patologie/eiaculazione_retrograda.htm#|archivedate=2008-02-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Disturbi sessuali Impotenza Eiaculazione precoce|url=http://www.psicosessuologia.it/site/index.php?mode=page&pagename=apfemm2&cat=sessuologia|accessdate=2020-12-25|publisher=Psicologa Psicoterapeuta Sessuologa a Firenze - Dott.ssa Fiorella Bado|language=it|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140131210433/http://www.psicosessuologia.it/site/index.php?mode=page&pagename=apfemm2&cat=sessuologia|archivedate=2014-01-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 治療 ==

逆行射精的治療取決於具體病因，直接作用於逆行射精的藥物只有很少的案例中才會用到，此外手術也很少使用。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Retrograde ejaculation - Symptoms and causes|url=https://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/retrograde-ejaculation/symptoms-causes/syc-20354890|accessdate=2020-12-25|work=Mayo Clinic|language=en}}</ref>

